Class BookHotelView

java.lang.Object
java.awt.Component
java.awt.Container
javax.swing.JComponent
javax.swing.JPanel
BookHotelView
All Implemented Interfaces:
ImageObserver, MenuContainer, Serializable, Accessible
public class BookHotelView extends JPanel
BookHotelView is a custom JPanel that represents the user interface for booking a hotel. It includes fields for inputting check-in and check-out dates, customer name, and a discount code. It also provides a list of available rooms and allows the user to confirm their booking. The panel is designed with several sub-panels to organize the layout of the interface components.
